N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 13 ยง 52.17 - Orders of the attorney general

State Regulations

All orders of the Attorney General shall be in writing and shall be filed with the

Department of Law, which shall cause certified copies thereof to be served upon the registrant. Notes
